sources.title: San Andreas Mega Quake | Full Action Disaster Movie
sources.description:
San Andreas Megaquake - Scientists discover the "Big One" is coming soon, and with it everything west of the San Andreas Fault will sink into the ocean. The scientists try to stop the quake, but as foreshocks turn California into chaos, it's a race against time.
2019.  Stars: Joseph Michael Harris, Christie Nicholls, Liz Fenning
